<section xml:id="soc" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" version="5.0">
    <title>Summary of changes</title>
    <section xml:id="pe-changes" condition="pe">
        <title>Version 4 F2 - 5 LTS</title>
        <formalpara>
            <title>Changes in product:</title>
            <para/>
        </formalpara>
        <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
                <para><olink targetdoc="syslog-ng-pe-guide-admin" targetptr="installing-syslog-ng-windows"/>,<olink targetdoc="syslog-ng-pe-guide-admin" targetptr="windows-limitations"/>, and <olink targetdoc="syslog-ng-pe-guide-admin" targetptr="configuring-sources-eventlog"/>has been added to the document.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Several macros that were available only in &agent; are now available in &abbrev; as well. These have been added to <olink targetdoc="syslog-ng-pe-guide-admin" targetptr="reference-macros"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The <parameter>allow-compress()</parameter> and <parameter>tls-required()</parameter> options have been documented in <olink targetdoc="syslog-ng-pe-guide-admin" targetptr="rltp-options"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The <parameter>use-syslogng-pid()</parameter> option has been documented.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The <parameter>cert-subject()</parameter> option has been documented in <olink targetdoc="syslog-ng-pe-guide-admin" targetptr="tlsoptions"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The <parameter>custom-domain()</parameter> option has been documented in <olink targetdoc="syslog-ng-pe-guide-admin" targetptr="global-option-custom-domain"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The <parameter>spoof-interface()</parameter> option of the <parameter>udp()</parameter> destination has been documented.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The <parameter>qout-size()</parameter> disk-buffer option has been documented.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The syslog-ng-ctl options <parameter>reload</parameter> and <parameter>stop</parameter> have been documented in <olink targetdoc="syslog-ng-pe-guide-admin" targetptr="syslog-ng-ctl.1"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The description of escaping special characters used in templates has been updated in <olink targetdoc="syslog-ng-pe-guide-admin" targetptr="configuring-macros"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The manual page of the pdbtool utility has been updated, and descriptions to missing options and commands has been added. For details, see <xref linkend="pdbtool.1"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The <parameter>tags()</parameter> option has been documented in <xref linkend="reference-source-internal"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The <parameter>expect-hostname</parameter> source flag has been documented.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The <parameter>--caps</parameter> option has been documented in <xref linkend="syslog-ng.8"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The <xref linkend="global-option-proto-template"/> and <xref linkend="global-option-file-template"/> global options have been documented.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="sql-option-session-statements"/> has been added to the document.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="template-function-indent-multi-line"/> has been added to the document.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The <parameter>allow-compress()</parameter> option has been documented. For details, see <xref linkend="tlsoptions"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>HP-UX 11v3 support on Itanium64 has been added to <xref linkend="supported-platforms"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
        <formalpara>
            <title>Changes in documentation:</title>
            <para/>
        </formalpara>
        <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
                <para>The synopsis and usage of the <parameter>facility()</parameter> and <parameter>priority()</parameter> filters have been corrected.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The default ports of the syslog drivers have been corrected.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Erroneous references to RFC5427 and RFC5428 have been removed.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Missing facility names have been added to <xref linkend="filter-facility"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The description of the <parameter>chain-hostnames</parameter> global option has been extended. For details, see <xref linkend="global-options-chain-hostnames"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The document index has been updated.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The descriptions of statistics types have been clarified in <xref linkend="chapter-log-statistics"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The description of pipe() has been clarified.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Descriptions of the <parameter>multiline-prefix</parameter> and <parameter>multiline-garbage</parameter> options have been removed from the sources that do not support them.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Clarified the use of double-quotes and special characters in <xref linkend="regular-expressions"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Added a note about unsupported column types to <xref linkend="configuring-sql-mssql"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The maximal number of worker-threads has been clarified in <xref linkend="chapter-multithreading"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Corrected a note about persistent message contexts in <xref linkend="patterndb-correlation"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Clarifications in <xref linkend="configuring-sql-oracle"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>A description of the <userinput>BOM</userinput> character has been added to <xref linkend="glossary-bom"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The description of the <parameter>delimiter</parameter> option of csv-parser() has been clarified. For details, see <xref linkend="csv-parser-delimiter"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>A few notes regarding kernel messages and file sources have been reorganized to <xref linkend="kernel-messages"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
    </section>
</section>
